Ask the user to enter a number
Create an array of months starting from January to December(Months= ["January", "February".....])
IF number is greater than 12, Ask the user to enter a number ranging from 1-12
ELSE
Display the respective month to the user(Months[number])

-----------OR ANOTHER METHOD----------
Ask the user to enter a number
IF number is greater than 12 THEN
Ask the user to enter a number ranging from 1-12
ELSE
  IF number = 1 THEN
  Display the month January
  ELSE 
  IF number = 2 THEN 
  Display the month February
  ELSE
  IF number = 3 THEN 
  Display the month March
  ELSE
  IF number = 4 THEN 
  Display the month April
  ELSE
  IF number = 5 THEN 
  Display the month May
  ELSE
  IF number = 6 THEN 
  Display the month June
  ELSE
  IF number = 7 THEN 
  Display the month July
  ELSE
  IF number = 8 THEN 
  Display the month August
  ELSE
  IF number = 9 THEN 
  Display the month September
  ELSE
  IF number = 10 THEN 
  Display the month October
  ELSE
  IF number = 11 THEN 
  Display the month November
  ELSE
  IF number = 12 THEN 
  Display the month December
